WEBVTT

00:03.815 --> 00:04.814
Richard.

00:05.887 --> 00:07.667
Okay, I'll carry your pack
all day long

00:07.767 --> 00:08.946
if you give me ten more minutes.

00:09.698 --> 00:11.198
Are you all right?

00:11.622 --> 00:12.922
Have a heart, Zedd.

00:15.353 --> 00:17.153
Richard, it's me, Michael.

00:23.076 --> 00:24.176
Michael.

00:25.087 --> 00:26.587
How did you--?

00:28.260 --> 00:29.560
How did I get here?

00:30.575 --> 00:33.275
Some guards found you at the bottom
of the cliff and carried you home.

00:33.422 --> 00:35.222
You've been out for two days.

00:35.715 --> 00:37.115
That's not true.

00:37.534 --> 00:38.734
Where's Zedd?

00:38.860 --> 00:40.846
Where's Kahlan?
How did I get through the boundary?

00:40.946 --> 00:42.725
You're not making sense,
you should be lying down.

00:42.825 --> 00:44.018
You had quite a fall.

00:44.939 --> 00:46.323
This is some
kind of trick, isn't it?

00:46.423 --> 00:47.223
Richard...

00:47.289 --> 00:48.570
Well, it's not going to work.

00:48.966 --> 00:50.566
I know it wasn't
Kahlan who killed Dad.

00:50.673 --> 00:52.497
I know it was Fane,
and you helped him!

00:52.597 --> 00:54.172
Richard,
what are you talking about?

00:54.718 --> 00:56.718
I'm talking about Dad dying

00:56.863 --> 00:58.163
right outside that door!

01:00.380 --> 01:02.280
I tried to stop the bleeding,
but it was too late.

01:04.215 --> 01:05.015
Dad...

01:08.032 --> 01:09.832
I felt the life go out of him.

01:12.211 --> 01:13.011
Richard!

01:14.688 --> 01:16.088
We saw the smoke.

01:17.031 --> 01:18.231
What happened?

01:19.457 --> 01:20.757
He's dead.

